title: No Diablo 4, Overwatch 2 This Year - Kinda Funny Games Daily 02.05.21
description:
Things I Learned from Mario's Butt' author Laura Kate Dale joins Greg to talk about #Diablo4 and #Overwatch2 not making it in 2021, Sony buying a stake in the parent company of #FromSoftware, and #MassEffect butts!   

Follow Laura: https://twitter.com/LaurakBuzz

00:00:00 - Start
00:03:00 - Housekeeping
Gamescast found the worst game of 2021, come see it.
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: GrahamOfLegend, David Meintel, Trent Berrie, Black Jack, Luiz Aguiar (@8bitLuiz), James Davis (@JamesDavisMakes), &The Nano Biologist
